added.title: Tyrannosaurus Wrecks
added.description: Thomas and the other Engines get to deliver some newly discovered dinosaur bones, but they must deliver them in the correct order for assembly, which isn't as easy as it sounds...
added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: The Super-Long Shortcut
added.description: When Gordon is unable to make an important delivery on his own, Thomas offers his help, but Gordon insists on second-guessing Thomas's every move.
added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: Caillou the Librarian/Caillou the Bookworm/Caillou the Storyteller
added.description: Caillou is excited about showing Rosie the ropes when they visit the library./Returning home from the library Caillou is very eager to sit down and enjoy his pirate book./It's a rainy day at playschool and the children can't go outside.

added.title: A Present for Mommy/Caillou the Chef/Caillou the Painter
added.description: Mommy's having a bad day - first she can't find her car keys, then she and Caillou have to shovel the car out, and then the car won't start!/Jeffrey and Jason are coming over for dinner - it's a make-your-own pizza party!/Caillou's got a brand new painting shirt and decides to paint something for Grandma.

added.title: Captain Caillou/The Loudest Noise/Caillou's First Wedding
added.description: Grandpa's got a surprise for Caillou on their trip to the park - it's a remote control sailboat!/Mommy sends Caillou to play outside because he's making too much noise and it's Rosie's nap time./Daddy and Mommy's friend Jonas is getting married.

added.title: Shoo, Shoo Bird, Fly Away!/Caillou's Road Trip/Caillou and the Dragon
added.description: When birds keep eating the seeds in Mommy and Caillou's newly planted garden, they come up with the idea of making a scarecrow./One fine day the family is going on a car trip./There's a special visitor at Caillou's playschool - a boy named Alan who has Down Syndrome.

added.title: Caillou's Surprise/A Surprise for Miss Martin/A Surprise Sleepover
added.description: When Caillou accidentally breaks Mommy's favorite cup, Grandma suggests they make her a new one./When Caillou finds out that Miss Martin's birthday is coming up, he wants to do something very special for her./Sarah is playing at Caillou's house when a sudden rainstorm causes a power outage.

added.title: Mad Mix Machine
added.description: Pocoyo finds a super duper machine that mixes objects and makes special new toys to play with. But when Pocoyo puts his friends' toys in the machine for fun, he upsets them. Eventually Pocoyo has to put things back to normal and then share his new magic machine with his friends so they can all enjoy it.

added.title: The Messy Guest
added.description: Pocoyo is having a lovely time playing with his friends but little does he realize that he's making a mess and leaving them to clear it all up! When he sees that his friends no longer want to play with him, he comes to understand the importance not only of having fun and making a mess, but of helping and clearing up too.

added.title: New on the Planet
added.description: Pocoyo is scared when a stranger appears in Pocoyoland, but he soon comes to realize that he needn't be scared of this little alien and they become friends.

added.title: Pocoyo's Present
added.description: Pocoyo has a beautifully wrapped up present but he won't open it. Elly is dying to know what's inside. She begs and pleads but when that fails she turns to desperate measures.

added.title: Elly's Ballet Class
added.description: Elly wants to be a prima ballerina with a troupe of other dancers so she tries to teach her friends to dance just like her. But she gets frustrated that they can't do it straight away and is very bossy. Finally everyone dances together in their own special way.

added.title: Mural
added.description: Sula and Amma are painting a mural when Bing and Flop arrive and help. Amma reminds Bing that when painting, it's important to remember to "Dip it... and... Wipe it" to stop the drips! But what will happen when Bing forgets to wipe his brush?

added.title: Hiding
added.description: Bing is helping Flop in Padget's shop when he decides to hide from Flop! But what will happen when Bing hides in Padget's store room and gets locked in?

added.title: Sandcastle
added.description: Bing and Flop are building sandcastles when Pando comes to help with Don the Dumpertruck! But what will happen when Pando realizes Don's starter key is being used as a decoration on Bing's sandcastle?

added.title: Acorns
added.description: Bing and Sula are collecting and counting acorns in the Howly Woods. But when they start to disappear, Flop explains that they need to stay mousy quiet to find out where they're going!

added.title: Jingly Shoes
added.description: Charlie really wants to try to walk and with the help of Bing's jingly shoes he takes his first steps! But what will happen when Coco suggests Charlie should keep them?

added.title: To Catch a Fly
added.description: When Findley watches a show about spiders eating flies, he thinks Lucas wants to eat him!

added.title: Sliding
added.description: Lucas and Findley find an ice cube. When Lucas rides the ice cube in the sink and falls down the drain, a scared Findley rallies to save him.

added.title: The Disappearing Mushler
added.description: Mush-Mush can't wait to show his tricks of forest illusion to everyone. But Amanita keeps ruining Mush-Mush's performance by figuring out all his tricks. Grrr! When Mush-Mush decides to do his famous 'Disappearing Mushable' trick on Truff, Truff really disappears! And now, Amanita and Mush-Mush must join forces to find their disappearing friend.

added.title: Power Outage
added.description: The Care Bears come to the aid of a group of Whiffles whose worries are blanketing their garden with such bad vibes that plants won't grow. When the Care Bear Stare isn't powerful enough to help, Grumpy comes to the rescue with the invention of a robotic Care Bear Stare amplifier.

added.title: The Mysterious Seepod
added.description: Chep has come across a new seedpod specimen. Mushpot warns him not to take it though. But the temptation is too much and Chep can't resist taking the seedpod and opening it to find it is full of itchy powder! Argh! Mush-Mush and Lilit do their best to help their friend, but it seems like the only way Chep can get rid of the itching is to ask Mushpot for a remedy.

added.title: Where Oh Where Has Our Funshine Gone?
added.description: When Funshine uses the Care Bears' work time to develop his latest comic book character, his creative playtime jeopardizes the success of the team's mission to a strange part of the Silver Lining.

added.title: Pig Who Cried Woof
added.description: Petunia fakes emergencies. But when a real one arises, no one believes her.

added.title: Daffy Did It!
added.description: Tweety blames Daffy for his mistake, and then has trouble living with the guilt of lying.

added.title: A Clean Sweep
added.description: Daffy tries to avoid cleaning up by sweeping his toys under a rug.

added.title: Picture This!
added.description: The babies create their own endings to fairytales.

added.title: Hair Cut-Ups
added.description: Lola is afraid of getting her first haircut.

added.title: Lonesome Lucas
added.description: Lucas wakes up in the middle of the night. How long can a night alone last?

added.title: I Can't See You
added.description: Lucas tries to beat Bodhi at Hide and Seek.

removed.title: All for One
removed.description: Pocoyo wants to play but Baby Bird is flying up in the sky, Pato and Octopus are helicoptering, Elly is jumping up into outer space and even little Caterpillar transforms into a butterfly and flutters away. Pocoyo feels left out so they get together to help him fly up in the sky along with them.

removed.title: Sleepover
removed.description: Bing & Coco are having a sleepover today! They mix up their bedtimes and Bing shows Coco his nightlight Owly. But what will happen when Coco turns all the lights out to show Bing what Amber, one of her Rainbow Fairy Mice, can do?

removed.title: House
removed.description: Bing is playing "Big Bad Wolf" today with Sula, Coco and Charlie and Bing gets to be the wolf! But what will happen when Bing wants to come into the brick house with everyone else?

removed.title: Monsterplant
removed.description: Bluster creates a mad scientist's monster from a clump of moss and sends it to scare the Whiffles away. The kindhearted Monsterplant just wants to be friends with them, but the Whiffles are frightened away by how he looks. Share and Dibble work together to show the Whiffles how nice Monsterplant is on the inside.

removed.title: The Breathtaking Bolly Show
removed.description: If Mush-Mush had Bolly's speed, he'd want everyone to see just how awesomely fast he was. But Bolly is different - he just likes to use his speed helping Mushables. So when Mush-Mush organizes a big stunt for Bolly, he refuses. He just doesn't like to show off. But Mush-Mush promised everyone a show so a show he will give them with Mush-Mush performing instead of Bolly! Gulp!

removed.title: Guess What?
removed.description: Pocoyo plays a game with us. He shows us a series of different extremely strange shapes and wants us to guess what they are. A fun guessing game, learning to look at things in different ways...

removed.title: Upside Down
removed.description: Pato gets stuck hanging upside down from the sky. Pocoyo and the friends try to help him down.

removed.title: Dizzy
removed.description: Bing wants to do spinning on the spinny chair so Pando pushes him superfast. But what will happen when Bing starts to feel too dizzy and wants to stop?

removed.description: Caillou is playing with the fridge magnets and learns lots of things about them./The whole family goes on a trip to the natural history museum to look at the dinosaurs./Caillou wants to play with both his friends Clementine and Xavier at the playschool playground.

removed.title: Mr Big Duck
removed.description: Pato is enjoying playing at being very grown up and doesn't want to join in the games with his friends. Eventually though, Pato and the others realize that playing with friends is much more fun than hanging around being 'cool'.

removed.title: Surprise Machine
removed.description: Bing and Sula are in Padget's Shop today when they discover the new surprise machine. But what will happen when Bing's surprise toy isn't the one he was hoping for?

removed.description: Clementine's big brother Billy has a new drum set and is having lots of fun playing as loud as he can./Caillou and his friends are very excited when a real marching band goes by the playschool./The playschool is having a talent show and Caillou wants to sing a song.

removed.title: Eggsellent Adventure
removed.description: Thomas and Percy have a difficult delivery - getting eggs and other cake ingredients safely to Vicarstown for their bake-off.

removed.title: Neon Beach Party
removed.description: Bluster and his Bad Crowd arrive at a lakeside beach for his summer vacation, unaware that the Care Bears are having their vacation on the opposite shore. Trapped inside Bluster's climate-control dome and forced to spend their vacations together, the Bears must find a way to make friends with their ill-tempered neighbors.

removed.title: Snowflakes/Caillou Shoots! He Scores!/Caillou goes Tobogganing
removed.description: Caillou eagerly awaits the first snowfall of winter, and imagines himself building the biggest snowman./Caillou wants to play hockey with Billy and the other big kids./Mommy can't find Caillou's toboggan for the playschool tobogganing trip.

removed.title: Band Together
removed.description: The babies learn about music and improvise their own orchestra.

removed.description: When the engines are delivering attractions to the annual Harwick Beach Carnival, a series of mistakes causes the precious Calliope to break. Luckily, the engines come up with a creative solution.

removed.title: Business as Unusual
removed.description: Bugs and Daffy open competing lemonade stands.

removed.title: Band of Friends
removed.description: Pocoyo meets a funny little red shape. At first it teases and hides from him, making him jump and chasing him around. But then it brings along its friends and together they put on a music and dancing show for Pocoyo and his gang.

removed.title: The Harder They Fall
removed.description: Bugs is embarrassed to admit he doesn't know how to skate.

removed.title: Mr. McStuffles
removed.description: Daffy doesn't want to give up his old toy, even after he's outgrown it.

removed.title: War of the Weirds
removed.description: Marvin the Martian comes to visit, and the babies learn to accept differences.

removed.title: Ice Lolly
removed.description: It's hot today so Bing and Flop are having yummy delicious ice pops from Gilly. But what will happen to their ice pops when Bing and Flop are rescuing Froggy from the swimming pool in the garden?

removed.title: Show and Tell/Caillou the Magician/Caillou's Castle
removed.description: Caillou has to decide on a nice surprise to bring to playschool for Show and Tell./Grandma shows Caillou a simple magic trick, which makes him decide to be a magician./Caillou wants to play castles and dragons, even though Gilbert isn't very keen on playing the dragon.

removed.description: Caillou is playing with Jeffrey and Jason when he gets accidentally pushed down./There's a new girl named Lee Wun in playschool, but she's so shy she won't talk to anybody./The whole family is on the way to the beach but accidentally ends up on a trail through a swamp.
